{"tid":2330234,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"世衛獲中方邀請赴武漢調查　中方：願與世衛加強合作","createTime":"2020-12-18T00:18:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-18T01:46:26.000Z","uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"1c249e5997195f87b2b4a3c94a0b1bf6b105bc5a","tid":2330234,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T00:18:33.000Z","msg":"世衛組織據報下月派專家組到中國，調查新型冠狀病毒的起源，在北京，外交部發言人汪文斌表示，中方願繼續與世衛加強合作，推進全球溯源工作。<br />\n<br />\n汪文斌說，自新冠疫情發生以來，中方本著開放和負責任的態度，率先同世衛組織開展溯源合作，世衛組織專家兩次到中國考察，中方專家和世衛及國際專家組也舉行多次視像交流，積極分享中國的溯源成果和抗疫經驗。中國與世衛的合作正穩步推進。<br />\n<br />\n路透社引述世衛專家組成員之一德國專家倫德茨表示，已開始與中方科學家商討，預計下月赴華，團隊可能從武漢開始調查，但詳細行程尚未確定。倫德茨表示，國際專家組此行目的是搜集資料，為未來疫情爆發做好準備，不是要找哪個國家來怪罪，整個調查行程預計4至5周，在行程結束後，專家會撰寫報告。"},{"pid":"375a2775ee386e395a4889f6354b1faf0028af5a","tid":2330234,"uid":283761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T00:19:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8202b1f1a611ae69c8e2b7627ddfedfef681d91e","tid":2330234,"uid":31946,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T00:20:00.000Z","msg":"又話唔係黎自武漢，但係就去搵起源...<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解唔係去外太空搵"},{"pid":"191c7072bc9ee5b5c887a93c9ad444b2754933ae","tid":2330234,"uid":70786,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T00:20:47.000Z","msg":"成個武漢生化實驗室俾中國軍方接管完成年有多先俾世衛去查<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ab851fa6ef06b01efb5306a59485d2d03c470e4","tid":2330234,"uid":84081,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T00:21:01.000Z","msg":"到時又畀個女仔做陪遊<br />\n4-5週幻幻團<br />\n<br />\n成年幾啦 金字塔都起到 仲有咩好查<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"277606ebaca7cd8311e2f4e4b6f3c91e62af1bbd","tid":2330234,"uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T00:21:08.000Z","msg":"調查報告都幫佢地寫好 武漢係爆發地非源頭<br />\n<br />\n拜登一月再入乞返世衛 條件係認武肺源自美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b7060f49e3ca359558ba17a1633dd6df749865f","tid":2330234,"uid":7323,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T00:21:13.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">過左成年先去，去做歷史考察啊。仆街黑奴譚德塞</span>"},{"pid":"c82980115345a9e35558468dc57881a76610e4d1","tid":2330234,"uid":84081,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"191c7072bc9ee5b5c887a93c9ad444b2754933ae","tid":2330234,"uid":70786,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T00:20:47.000Z","msg":"成個武漢生化實驗室俾中國軍方接管完成年有多先俾世衛去查<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T00:22:23.000Z","msg":"直情提供「證據」<br />\n證明澳洲經涷肉傳播畀武漢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f55373cc5f833ef88eafec45c4907976e1e9274e","tid":2330234,"uid":214309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T00:23:26.000Z","msg":"應該等武肺消失先好去嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4ac3a00c387be45b4d7427c477397c49b806bd8","tid":2330234,"uid":364767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T00:33:38.000Z","msg":"世乜鬼衛吖！ 支那衛就真！"},{"pid":"4eb68c4cbeb0a1bf97da32101bf220cf6eddedff","tid":2330234,"uid":254383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T00:36:15.000Z","msg":"抗疫成功典範"},{"pid":"63f710ab09683be50f0689fcde0a3b396879af3c","tid":2330234,"uid":62749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T00:38:38.000Z","msg":"